Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All my parents ever did was fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, I said!\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shut up, bitch!\N- Hands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After my mother got divorced,\Nshe'd bring lots of men home,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they pushed me\Nout of the way every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother would never listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be a gangster, shoplifter and fighter...\Nthey all called me a god of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, he... he alone would...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Inaba! You're here today, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give her a hug\Nsometimes, too? She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I have to change myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matogi... kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked you, Haru!\NGo out with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that too direct?\NI can't say that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miku. Don't let Inaba-san\Ntake him from you no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to change myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:58.25,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cha cha fantasy.\N{\i1}Cha cha fantasy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:04.19,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside of me, the power of fire sleeps.\N{\i1}Watashi no nake ni hi no chikara ga nemutteru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.19,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cha cha fantasy.\N{\i1}Cha cha fantasy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:12.73,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,To make the dream come true once again.\N{\i1}Mou ichido yume wo kanaeru tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:20.57,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Usagi-chan de Cue!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:24.17,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,The days when we laughed like fools.\N{\i1}Baka mitai ni waratta hibi wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:28.31,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,The memories where we cried till it hurt.\N{\i1}Itai kurai naita kioku wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:31.88,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,If they were all lies,\N{\i1}Zenbu itsuwari nara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:36.89,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,My nature would be sad.\N{\i1}Watashi rashi sa ga kanashii ne{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:42.59,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when have you\N{\i1}Aimai ni ne itsu kara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:52.60,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Remembered only how to give up?\N{\i1}Akirameru koto dake wo oboeta no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:54.30,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back. Just get.\N{\i1}Get back just get{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.24,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cha cha fantasy.\N{\i1}Cha cha fantasy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:58.24,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Something is different."\N{\i1}Nani ka ga chigau{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:02.21,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,When I have that feeling...\N{\i1}Sonna omoi ga aru no nara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.21,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Change my destiny!\N{\i1}Change my destiny{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:08.35,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,People give in all the time.\N{\i1}Itsu datte hito wa merikonde{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.19,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cha cha fantasy.\N{\i1}Cha cha fantasy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.22,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Like my heart...\N{\i1}Kono mune mitai na{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:16.19,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,With the future I've always looked for.\N{\i1}Zutto sagashiteta mirai to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:18.23,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Change my destiny.\N{\i1}Change my destiny{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:24.60,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one real me.\N{\i1}Hontou no watashi wa hitotsu mikakeru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool, your opponents are\Nincredibly tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.82,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Public Welfare Bureau
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Assembly of the\NPublic Welfare Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you haven't heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This remote self-governing area\Nis organized under the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange things are happening\Nin this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:04:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is, beings are merging.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't predict what\Nmerged beings will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a good idea to do nothing\Nand cover up the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What should we do?\N- Catch them and experiment on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Experiment on them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we should make this world\Nnormal again... without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:38.94,Headband,,0000,0000,0000,,= Knowledge =
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To follow up on this, they have made\Nan example of this district.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai is to be a special district,\Nwith no merged beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't to let it happen there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wouldn't let it happen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until Mimika appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a spy, a running dog of the\NGeneral Assembly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality, I {\i1}am{\i0} a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-you're also a merged being?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:02.40,Headband,,0000,0000,0000,,= Cool =
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell merged beings,\Nso I've been looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're betraying your own kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:09.10,Headband,,0000,0000,0000,,= Sober? =
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only way\NI could remain alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are abandoned so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.57,Headband,,0000,0000,0000,,= Embarrassed =
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the huge guy that\Nlooked like a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Dekao is an enforcement cyborg\Nsent by the Department...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an Admonisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Then, Mimika, is...\N- Umm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why do merged beings happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:36.90,Headband,,0000,0000,0000,,= Explaining =
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merging happens when someone loses\Ntheir mind and their humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're lonely people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They get more and more lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if they can't handle it,\Nthey become a merged being.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimika! You came home ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I have to... change myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:05:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-is this strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-no... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-cu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-- you look odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! Can't you say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, is she really Mimika or Inaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do merged beings happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They get more and more lonely,\Nand if they can't handle it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:07:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I've never seen\Nher play with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have captured all the merged beings\Nin our test district.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but something is not right\Nin the most important place of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of Inaba Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have received a report\Nfrom the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They found out that merged beings\Ncan affect humans with telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot lose this world because of\None little merged being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:51.03,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Summer Thank You Sale!\NClothing And Goods 30-50% Off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.51,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,GAP Sale 60% Off!\NFlower Shop Opens Until 10PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A G-cup... that's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, but wouldn't that be okay?\N- That's really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it might not be big enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I dragged all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh! Haru will fall head over heels for this!\N- What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Because I like him! I like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we go to bed together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-sleep together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come here Mimika.\NLet's sleep together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Haru! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That small, tiny, fluffy, soft, cute tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it'll melt if I touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And those cute, smooth, thin,\Nattractive, lovely long ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those melting front teeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're so passionate that they remind\Nme of the Caribbean Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, an ultra\Nsuper-dangerous body...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that makes me nosebleed and drool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you are the perfect person for\Nsomeone like me, who loves animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy! Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you two been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you really a rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a rabbit, so Haru adores you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haru is worried about you\Nand keeps you at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, so I'm on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also love animals as much as anyone,\Nso I've kept quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm envious of you because\Nyou're always with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's never thought of me as a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've always thought of him as a boy,\Nand we were always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Haru much better than you do,\Nso I really love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Miku-chan!\N- Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimika-chan, I know you don't mean\Nto do any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm! Inaba Mikami! Now there's\Nnowhere for you to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have completely\Noccupied this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who are you?\N- Customers, we're just customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You useless wretches!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good! We can get out\Nthrough there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time we'll finish our duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Never mind that, just go!\N- But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, get Miku\Nout of here somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I'll get Miku out of here, and then\NI'll definitely come back to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never underestimate a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, where do you\Nthink you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Chou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:10.29,Headband,,0000,0000,0000,,= Chou =
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Amazing!\N- They're monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're no match for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:33.88,Headband,,0000,0000,0000,,= Chou =
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chou... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! I don't want you\Nto misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They betrayed me, and this is\Nhow I pay them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Get out of here!\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let's... stop now.\N- What-nya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both merged beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not the same.\NWe're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have Matogi and Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father's a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's despicable!\N- A murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Koshka. Where's Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take it to the home with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't go without Koshha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koshha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had strength, I wouldn't need\Nanyone to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was strong, I wouldn't need\Npeople to be kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koshka, it's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- They tricked us!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Abumidah! They intend to\Nget rid of all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're blaming this attack on us\Nand using it to destroy us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake!\NWe're useless to them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koshka... you're also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What happened?!\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koshka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koshka, come here.\NIt's time to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I want to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:16:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be strong, don't you?\NCome, Koshka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Koshka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekao again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.44,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.17,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy\NDestroy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inaba Mikami. Koshka. Destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koshka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing,\Nyou stupid rabbit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the strength to talk,\Nstand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:39.32,Headband,,0000,0000,0000,,= Fortune Family =
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we can't go down any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no choice. Let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's finally running out of ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kind of like the last scene\Nin an old movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who do you think\Nyou're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should go about now, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-don't make me your partner by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-what are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inaba-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I can't get even close to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... even if you could get close to him,\Nyou couldn't beat him with that pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't... isn't there something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... a high-voltage cable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! How should I fight him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way, stupid rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koshka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:18:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as... that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.64,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki's Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I said that I wanted something...\NI would get scolded... get beaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't... wish for things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.74,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I will be hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wish for things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That if Haru has come to like Miku, you'll\Nbecome an unwanted child again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, are you okay if they die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is most important to you now?\NWhat is most precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that what you do\Nis meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow... tomorrow will surely be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reach them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to want things...\Nand to wish for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bye-bye!\N- See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inaba-san didn't come to school\Ntoday after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The newspaper and TV said that\Nthere were no dead or missing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matogi, I like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are... Mimika's gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dinnertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I a dog or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay now. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I need to look like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.25,0:22:32.48,Headband,,0000,0000,0000,,= Ha? =
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:37.45,Headband,,0000,0000,0000,,= Preaching =
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you live as Inaba Mikami,\Nthe Public Welfare Bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and other institutions from all over the\Ncountry will come looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the best evidence for the\Nexistence of merged beings in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you have to run away\Nas long as you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will chase us for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:01.88,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Your true feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.31,0:23:05.78,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,I am another persona inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All thoughts aren't just those\Nof a rabbit, but your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'll go back after all.\N- H-hey, Inaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who comes, I'll beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:22.06,Headband,,0000,0000,0000,,= Unbelievable! =
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey... huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:37.88,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more precious to me than anyone.\N{\i1}Dare yori daiji ni omotte iru no ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:31.07,Headband2,,0000,0000,0000,,= A Good Time to Depart =
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones who can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.45,0:23:50.96,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it well, so I disguise it with a smile again.\N{\i1}Jouzu ni iezu ni mata egao de gomakasu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:24:01.27,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing shaking in your eyes...\N{\i1}Anata no hitomi no naka de yureru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:11.55,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it right now.\N{\i1}Ima watashi ga wakaranai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:18.52,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I like you, the more confused I become.\N{\i1}Suki ni naru hodo fuan ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.05,0:24:25.29,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,But my heart understands.\N{\i1}Kokoro na no ni wakatteru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.66,0:24:31.83,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can say everything that's on my mind.\N{\i1}Omoi no sumete tsutaenareru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.10,0:24:43.28,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even things that can't be expressed in words.\N{\i1}Kotoba wa nai koto mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.61,0:24:56.73,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing on a road that's hazy from the setting sun.\N{\i1}Yuuhi ni nijinda machi ni tatazumeba{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.29,0:25:09.80,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just makes me want to cry.\N{\i1}Chiisa na jibun ni tada nakitaku naru dake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.97,0:25:21.82,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,My shivering love will reach you, right?\N{\i1}Furueru ai wa todoite iru no ne{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.22,0:25:30.39,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand.\N{\i1}Anata ni wakaranai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.76,0:25:37.40,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I like you, the more confused I become.\N{\i1}Suki ni naru hodo fuan ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.93,0:25:44.17,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,And even so, my heart wants to understand.\N{\i1}Kokoro dakedo wakaritai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.54,0:25:50.71,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I put the pieces of my feelings together\N{\i1}Omoi no kakera ima tsunaida{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.98,0:26:02.16,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gently with these hands.\N{\i1}Yasashii sono te kara{\i0}
